      <title>一些关于hexo的快速指令</title>
      <link href="/2024/10/17/%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8Ehexo%E7%9A%84%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4/"/>
      <url>/2024/10/17/%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8Ehexo%E7%9A%84%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="适用性">适用性</h2><p>Windows系统</p><h2 id="前言">前言</h2><p>本文是关于Hexo博客维护的一些技巧，可以节省一定时间</p><blockquote><p>注：本文中出现的[BlogRoot]均指你的博客根目录</p></blockquote><h2 id="目的">目的</h2><p>通过bat批处理文件实现博客后台快速：</p><ol><li><a href="#%E6%B8%85%E9%99%A4%E7%BC%93%E5%AD%98">清除缓存</a></li><li><a href="#%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95">本地测试</a></li><li><a href="#%E4%B8%8A%E4%BC%A0%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99">上传网站</a></li><li><a href="#%E6%89%93%E5%BC%80%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99">打开网站</a></li><li><a href="#%E6%96%B0%E5%BB%BA%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0">新建文章</a></li><li><a href="#%E6%96%B0%E5%BB%BA%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2">新建页面</a></li></ol><h2 id="实现">实现</h2><h3 id="写在前面">写在前面</h3><p>新建所有的bat文件均为<strong>ANSI编码</strong>，否则会出现<strong>中文乱码</strong>现象</p><p>所有文件双击运行即可</p><h3 id="清除缓存">清除缓存</h3><p>新建[BlogRoot]\清除缓存.bat</p><p>内容为：</p><figure class="highlight bat"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">start</span> <span class="built_in">cmd</span>.exe /k &quot;@<span class="built_in">echo</span> off &amp;&amp; hexo cl &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">echo</span>. &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">echo</span> 已清理缓存 &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">pause</span> &amp;&amp; <span class="keyword">exit</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="本地测试">本地测试</h3><p>新建[BlogRoot]\本地测试.bat</p><p>内容为：</p><figure class="highlight bat"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">start</span> <span class="built_in">cmd</span>.exe /k &quot;@<span class="built_in">echo</span> off &amp;&amp; hexo cl &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">echo</span>. &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">echo</span> 已清理缓存 &amp;&amp; hexo s &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">pause</span> &amp;&amp; <span class="keyword">exit</span>&quot;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">start</span> http://localhost:<span class="number">4000</span>/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="上传网站">上传网站</h3><p>新建[BlogRoot]\上传网站.bat</p><p>内容为：</p><figure class="highlight bat"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">start</span> <span class="built_in">cmd</span>.exe /k &quot;@<span class="built_in">echo</span> off &amp;&amp; hexo cl &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">echo</span>. &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">echo</span> 已清理缓存 &amp;&amp; hexo d &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">echo</span>. &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">echo</span> 指令已完成 如出错请检查配置 &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">pause</span> &amp;&amp; <span class="keyword">exit</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="打开网站">打开网站</h3><p>新建[BlogRoot]\打开网站.bat</p><p>内容为：</p><figure class="highlight bat"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">start</span> https://example.com/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>注：其中**“<a href="http://example.com">example.com</a>”**更换为你自己的域名</p></blockquote><h3 id="新建文章">新建文章</h3><p>新建[BlogRoot]\新建文章.bat</p><p>内容为：</p><figure class="highlight bat"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cls</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">set</span> /p t1=&quot;请输入文章文件名：&quot; </span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">start</span> <span class="built_in">cmd</span>.exe /k &quot;hexo n <span class="variable">%t1%</span> &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">echo</span>. &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">echo</span> 已在 source/_posts 目录下生成文件：<span class="variable">%t1%</span>.<span class="built_in">md</span> 与 资源文件夹： <span class="variable">%t1%</span> &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">pause</span> &amp;&amp; <span class="keyword">exit</span>&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="新建页面">新建页面</h3><p>新建[BlogRoot]\新建页面.bat</p><p>内容为：</p><figure class="highlight bat"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cls</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">set</span> /p t2=&quot;请输入独立页面文件名：&quot;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">start</span> <span class="built_in">cmd</span>.exe /k &quot;hexo n page <span class="variable">%t2%</span> &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">echo</span>. &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">echo</span> 已在 source 目录下生成一个文件夹： <span class="variable">%t2%</span> 并在文件夹内创建了文件： index.<span class="built_in">md</span> &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">pause</span> &amp;&amp; <span class="keyword">exit</span>&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="快捷下载">快捷下载</h3><p><a href="https://tmp.link/f/6710ed326c947">文件下载链接</a></p><blockquote><p>注：其中“打开网页”文件中的**“dg-kc.top”**更换为你自己的域名</p></blockquote>]]></content>
      
      
