        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="适用性">适用性</h2><p><strong>AnZhiYu主题1.6.14</strong></p><h2 id="问题">问题</h2><p>在修改主题配置文件中</p><p>theme_color.toc_color</p><p>发现在深色模式下更改<strong>未生效</strong></p><h2 id="解决办法">解决办法</h2><p>修改[BlogRoot]\themes\anzhiyu\source\css_layout\sidebar.styl</p><p>将<strong>所有</strong></p><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">color</span>: <span class="built_in">var</span>(--anzhiyu-lighttext);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>更改为</p><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">color</span>: <span class="number">#ffffff</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>**注：**其中&quot;#ffffff&quot;为你想更改的十六进制颜色（不可省略）</p></blockquote><p>最后执行</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>打开<a href="http://localhost:4000/">http://localhost:4000/</a> 即可看到效果</p>]]></content>
      
      
